try{
    // Statment which can throw an exception
}catch(ExceptionName exceptionVariable) {
    // Catch | Handle the exception here
}finally {
    // Will be executed irrespective of whether 
    // an exception is thrown or not
}

1. Checked | Compile-time Exceptions
2. Unchecked | Runtime-time Exceptions

A-> throws -> Handle exception somewhere else
B-> throw  -> throw an exception